<para style="p">A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />To you, Yahweh, I cry out; my rock, do not ignore me.</para>

<para style="q1">If you do not respond to me, I will join those who go down to the grave.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Hear the sound of my pleading when I call for help from you,</para>

<para style="q1">when I lift up my hands toward your most holy place!</para>
